{
  "stem": "14091.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And he was four at that time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And my younger sister-- I mean, the younger, not me, the younger of my two oldest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "She had a little girl who was Mary, Miriam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] You could imagine our reunion.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] My mother became violent.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And she screamed at my sister that we came back.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And she begged her, she really begged her.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And she almost made her do it, to go back again in hiding.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "I didn't listen.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I said, whatever you do to me, I'm not going.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "But she arranged that my sister, Celia went back with Piotr to Lapuszyno.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "And she was there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "From that time on, I understood that she wasn't hiding.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "She was in the house, posing as a Polish niece of their family.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] In Glebokie ghetto was also so very, very hard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "They used to take actions every other day.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "An action of older people, take them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "And they would surround them, bring them to [INAUDIBLE], where the main pits were constantly open.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "Because they used to bring many people, and shot them, and just throw in.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "They never closed them, even.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Then they had actions of children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "When I came there, food wasn't any.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "So they put me-- they assigned me.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "Every day, I had to go and eat in somebody else's house.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And somehow, I became-- either the dirt, or the leeches, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I had-- I had scabies.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And they were so deep.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "They were eating me up.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "My hands, I couldn't hold my fingers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "They were like blisters on my fingers, between my fingers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And I was panicked by terrible, terrible lice.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "I had it all over.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And whatever it was done to me, they-- I couldn't get rid of that.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
